<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend_Date constructor  Zend_Date::now() is calling without $locale. (line 184)</p>

<p>If your browser doesn't send a HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE header and you don't pass date to Zend_Date then Zend_Locale will raise an exception "Autodetection of Locale has been failed!".</p>

    </div>
</div>

