            <p>This is only the case</p>

<ul><li>If the browser does not send the LANGUAGE Header</li>
<li>And you have not set a default locale within Zend_Locale or your bootstrap file</li>
<li>And your Environment does not provide a locale</li>
<li>And you are using a release below 7357</li>
</ul>
